type: software
title: "ConfusionMapper: A Python Tool for AI-Assisted Distractor Classification and Inter-Rater Reliability Computation in Cognitive Error Taxonomy Research"
version: 1.0.0
date-released: "2026-06-10"
authors:
  - family-names: Maurya
    given-names: Manik
